{"id":5218,"date":"2026-03-17T08:19:10","date_gmt":"2026-03-17T02:49:10","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/?page_id=5218"},"modified":"2026-04-28T12:11:59","modified_gmt":"2026-04-28T06:41:59","slug":"chapter-11-11-the-symptoms-of-conditioned-and-liberated-living-entities","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/","title":{"rendered":"Chapter : 11.11 &#8211; The Symptoms of Conditioned and Liberated Living Entities"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/1\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5216\">SB 11.11.1&nbsp;\u2013&nbsp;Nature of Jiva as marginal, small &amp; conscious never changes&nbsp;in bondage &amp; liberated state !&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/2\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5226\">SB 11.11.2 \u2013 Jiva\u2019s misconceptions about material world &amp; the only way to get out of it !&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/3\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5229\">SB 11.11.3 \u2013 Maya shakti\u2019s arrangement for bondage &amp; liberation &amp;&nbsp;cit&nbsp;shakti\u2019s influence in&nbsp;prema!&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/4\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5233\">SB 11.11.4 \u2013 Jiva\u2019s real identity and goal based on its state in material and spiritual existence !&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/5\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5237\">SB_11.11.5 \u2013 Fundamental principle in&nbsp;Vaidhi&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Raganuga&nbsp;bhakti &amp;&amp; astonishing bhakti&nbsp;process !&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/6\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5241\">SB 11.11.6 \u2013 Jiva can give up eating the fruits by experiencing the highest fruit of all \u2013&nbsp;Krsna !&nbsp;<\/a><br><br><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/7\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5252\">SB 11.11.7 \u2013 Vaishnavas &amp; Mayavadis vision about oneness &amp; difference in Supreme Absolute Truth !<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/8\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5247\">SB 11.11.8-Being humble &amp; surrender to Guru \u2013 way to get confidential &amp; most confidential knowledge!&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/11\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5256\">SB 11.11.11 \u2013 Effort &amp; result of karma (hard, bondage), jnana (trouble, liberation) &amp; bhakti (easy, prema)!&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/12-13\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5259\">SB 11.11.12~13 \u2013 Bhakti \u2013 the complete, easy &amp; blissful process to realize atma &amp; Supreme Lord !&nbsp;<\/a><br><br><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/14\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5264\">SB 11.11.14 &#8211; Prema bhakta&#8217;spranas, senses, mind, intelligence, gross body are saturated with prema!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/15\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5267\">SB 11.11.15 \u2013 Secondary result of Bhakti (destruction of suffering) is the primary goal of&nbsp;Jnana !&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/16-17\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5271\">SB 11.11.16~17 \u2013 Follow the instructions of advanced devotees, do not imitate !&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/18\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5274\">SB 11.11.18 \u2013 Karma, jnana, yoga \u2013 the useless endeavors which never give complete satisfaction for atma!&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/19\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5277\">SB 11.11.19 \u2013&nbsp;Srimad&nbsp;Bhagavatam \u2013 simplest presentation of the final truth &amp; the&nbsp;parampara&nbsp;system !&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/20\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5300\">SB 11.11.20 \u2013 All avatars are one with&nbsp;Krsna&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Krsna, the full&nbsp;moon !&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/21\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5306\">SB 11.11.21&nbsp;\u2013&nbsp;Without desire for knowledge, one cannot get knowledge &amp; practice bhakti to fix on&nbsp;the&nbsp;Lord&nbsp;!&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/22\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5309\">SB 11.11.22 \u2013 Pure bhakti cannot be equated with mixed bhakti &amp; it is superior to&nbsp;sak\u0101ma&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;ni\u1e63k\u0101ma&nbsp;!&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/23-24\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5318\">SB 11.11.23~24-Varnashrama duties coated with bhakti\/bhakti mixed with material desire are not pure!&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/25\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5356\">SB 11.11.25 \u2013 Pure devotee\u2019s association in any form purifies, best is to get knowledge of&nbsp;worship !&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/26-27\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5366\">SB 11.11.26~27-Knowledge on specific spiritual&nbsp;goal&nbsp;&amp; various&nbsp;process&nbsp;help to choose proper process!&nbsp;<\/a><br><br><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/28\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5371\">SB 11.11.28 &#8211; Special quality of Svayam Bhagavan Krsna &#8211; Sweet relationship with His devotees !<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/29-32\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5374\">SB 11.11.29~32-Vaishnava qualities are unlimited &amp; constitutional to&nbsp;bhakti,&nbsp;surrender is primary!&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/33\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5379\">SB 11.11.33 \u2013 Worship of one specific form develops greater&nbsp;prema&nbsp;than worshipping multiple forms!&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/34-41\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5387\">SB 11.11.34~41 \u2013 Result of engaging senses in&nbsp;angas&nbsp;of bhakti with pure, mixed &amp; without devotion!&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/42\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5393\">SB 11.11.42 \u2013 All worship is meant for Supreme Lord, best is worship of Vaishnavas as Supreme Lord !&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/43-45\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5396\">SB 11.11.43-45-Devotees prefer direct worship, still they respect all &amp; aware of all pervading Lord!&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/46\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5401\">SB 11.11.46 \u2013 Krsna is superior to Brahman &amp; all&nbsp;Vishnus. His pastimes&nbsp;attracts&nbsp;all types of&nbsp;yogis !&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/47\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5404\">SB_11.11.47 \u2013 Purify Varnashrama duties with proper mentality, remembrance of Lord &amp;&nbsp;sadhu&nbsp;sevaya&nbsp;!&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/sb\/11\/11\/48\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"5411\">SB 11.11.48 &#8211; Rely on sadhu sanga to understand &amp; practice Bhakti \u2013 the conclusion of all scriptures !<br><\/a><br><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>SB 11.11.1&nbsp;\u2013&nbsp;Nature of Jiva as marginal, small &amp; conscious never changes&nbsp;in bondage &amp; liberated state !&nbsp; SB 11.11.2 \u2013 Jiva\u2019s misconceptions about materia